channel.description:
[B]Why i released it:[/B]This was a project that died :\ got bored of coding. Was busy with irl things.
[B]Source I used:[/B]X5 (based on rune unlimitate)
[B]Some features:[/B] All godswords added All godsword specials added with the right gfx Added Saradomin Sword + spec (double hit, lightning) All dragon weapon specials work Stable source Has skills such as (thieving,wcing,cooking,runecrafting,fishing,crafting,herblore,fletching). Fightcaves Prayer Added following but too glitchy so i took out. staff making quest - by x5 Added cats thingy lol - by forgot who name.. Most doors work Fixed the 2h bug (cant have 2h weapon with shield) Added fully working 1 v 1 combat (added in varrock, dont know why lol just move it to edge) Made things undtradeable + put up X. (firecapes,torso, ect.) Added Full bandos Added Full armadyl Added all 3rd age items Broken barrows + npc that fixes it. fixed some bugs with combat. Added skulls but wont release that yet. Made all bonuses for weapons and armor ect. perfect Range projectiles Working ::banuser and ::unban Range farcast Weapon animations Weapon interfaces NPC aggression NPC face you in combat you face the npc + person you attack Barrows with killing the brothers then clicking the the chest getting random items such as blood runes, all barrows pieces, all runes, ect. Working gnome glider - by x5 :whistle: and much more.
